svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down w-3 h-3 transition-transform\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button><button class=\"relative px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 text-white/70 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5\">Services<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down w-3 h-3 transition-transform\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></button><a class=\"px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors rounded-full hover:bg-white/5\" href=\"/es/workshop\">Workshop</a></nav><div class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-4 flex-shrink-0\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white/70 hover:text-white transition-colors px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full hover:bg-white/5\" href=\"/en\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg> <!-- -->EN</a><a class=\"px-5 py-2 rounded-full bg-[#F2D3AC] text-[#131926] text-sm font-bold active:scale-[0.97] transition-transform duration-200\" href=\"/es/contact\">Contact HQ</a></div><button class=\"lg:hidden p-2 text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></header><main class=\"flex-1\"><div class=\"flex flex-col bg-[#F2F2F2]\"><section class=\"relative min-h-screen flex flex-col justify-center overflow-hidden bg-[#0B0F19]\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none\" style=\"transform:none\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center\" style=\"background-image:url(https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1486406146926-c627a92ad1ab?q=80&amp;w=2070&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop)\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0B0F19] via-[#0B0F19]/80 to-[#162D59]/50\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[#0B0F19]/40 backdrop-blur-[2px]\"></div></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 z-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none\"><div class=\"absolute -top-[20%] -right-[10%] w-[60%] h-[60%] rounded-full bg-[#0511F2] mix-blend-screen blur-[140px]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.8)\"></div><div class=\"absolute -bottom-[20%] -left-[10%] w-[50%] h-[50%] rounded-full bg-[#A65E44] mix-blend-screen blur-[160px]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.8)\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(242,242,242,0.03)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(242,242,242,0.03)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:4rem_4rem] [mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse_60%_60%_at_50%_50%,#000_70%,transparent_100%)]\"></div></div><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 pt-20\" style=\"opacity:1;transform:none\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl space-y-8\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center space-x-3 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-[15px] text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-[#F2D3AC]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><span class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#F2D3AC] animate-pulse\"></span><span>Arasue Horizon Group</span></div><h1 class=\"text-6xl md:text-8xl font-playfair tracking-tight leading-tight text-[#F2F2F2]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\">La perspectiva lo cambia todo.</h1><p class=\"text-xl md:text-3xl text-[#F2F2F2]/70 max-w-2xl font-medium font-inter\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\">El mundo se mueve rápido, pero nosotros miramos más allá. Arasue Horizon es la matriz estratégica que conecta mercados, capitales e industrias globales con una visión clara y de largo alcance. No solo gestionamos el presente; diseñamos el mapa del mañana.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-6 pt-12\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(40px)\"><a class=\"relative group overflow-hidden px-8 py-4 rounded-full bg-[#F2D3AC] text-[#162D59] font-bold text-lg active:scale-[0.97] transition-all w-full sm:w-auto text-center\" href=\"/es/forge\"><span class=\"relative z-10\">Explora nuestro Ecosistema</span><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-white\"></div></a><a class=\"relative group overflow-hidden px-8 py-4 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-black/20 backdrop-blur-[10px] text-[#F2F2F2] font-bold text-lg hover:border-white/30 active:scale-[0.97] transition-all w-full sm:w-auto text-center\" href=\"#portfolio\"><span class=\"relative z-10\">Explorar Portafolio</span><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-white/5 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"></div></a></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-24 border-y border-[#162D59]/10 bg-[#F2F2F2]\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"mb-8 text-xs font-mono text-[#162D59]/50 uppercase\">[Telemetry] Location: <!-- -->US<!-- --> | Currency: <!-- -->USD<!-- --> | System: <!-- -->metric</div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-x-8 gap-y-16\"><div class=\"flex flex-col space-y-4 border-l-[1px] border-[#162D59]/20 pl-6 relative group cursor-default\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute left-[-1px] top-0 bottom-0 w-[2px] bg-[#A65E44] origin-top\" style=\"transform:scaleY(0)\"></div><div class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-playfair font-black tracking-tighter text-[#162D59]\"><span>0</span></div><div class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#162D59]/60 font-semibold font-inter\">Divisiones Activas</div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col space-y-4 border-l-[1px] border-[#162D59]/20 pl-6 relative group cursor-default\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute left-[-1px] top-0 bottom-0 w-[2px] bg-[#A65E44] origin-top\" style=\"transform:scaleY(0)\"></div><div class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-playfair font-black tracking-tighter text-[#162D59]\"><span>0+</span></div><div class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#162D59]/60 font-semibold font-inter\">Proyectos Globales</div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col space-y-4 border-l-[1px] border-[#162D59]/20 pl-6 relative group cursor-default\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute left-[-1px] top-0 bottom-0 w-[2px] bg-[#A65E44] origin-top\" style=\"transform:scaleY(0)\"></div><div class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-playfair font-black tracking-tighter text-[#162D59]\"><span>$0M USD</span></div><div class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#162D59]/60 font-semibold font-inter\">Millones en Valor Generado</div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col space-y-4 border-l-[1px] border-[#162D59]/20 pl-6 relative group cursor-default\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"absolute left-[-1px] top-0 bottom-0 w-[2px] bg-[#A65E44] origin-top\" style=\"transform:scaleY(0)\"></div><div class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-playfair font-black tracking-tighter text-[#162D59]\"><span>0</span></div><div class=\"text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[#162D59]/60 font-semibold font-inter\">Oficinas Globales</div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"py-48 px-6 bg-[#0B0F19] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden border-y border-[#162D59]/30\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center space-y-8\" style=\"opacity:0.3;transform:scale(0.8)\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center space-x-3 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-[15px] text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-[#F2D3AC] mb-8\"><span class=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#F2D3AC] animate-pulse\"></span><span>Filosofía Operativa</span></div><h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-playfair tracking-tight text-[#F2F2F2] leading-tight\"><span class=\"block mb-2\">No seguimos tendencias.</span><span class=\"block text-[#A65E44] italic mb-6\">Construimos infraestructura.</span></h2><p class=\"text-xl md:text-2xl text-[#F2F2F2]/60 font-inter max-w-3xl mx-auto font-light tracking-wide\">El capital es solo una herramienta. La excelencia operativa es el resultado.</p></div></div><section class=\"py-32 px-6 container mx-auto\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center\"><div class=\"aspect-square bg-[#162D59]/5 rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden relative\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-[#162D59]/20 to-transparent z-10\"></div><img alt=\"Corporate Vision\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover grayscale opacity-80\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 50vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507679799987-c73779587ccf%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D1000%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507679799987-c73779587ccf%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D1000%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507679799987-c73779587ccf%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D1000%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507679799987-c73779587ccf%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D1000%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507679799987-c73779587ccf%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D1000%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507679799987-c73779587ccf%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D1000%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507679799987-c73779587ccf%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D1000%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507679799987-c73779587ccf%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D1000%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507679799987-c73779587ccf%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D1000%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507679799987-c73779587ccf%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D1000%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><div class=\"space-y-8\"><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-playfair tracking-tight text-[#162D59]\">Impulsando la Innovación</h2><p class=\"text-xl text-[#162D59]/70 leading-relaxed font-inter\">En Arasue Horizon, creemos en el poder de la excelencia diversificada. Al incubar y escalar subsidiarias especializadas, creamos un ecosistema robusto donde la tecnología, los medios y los bienes convergen.</p><p class=\"text-xl text-[#162D59]/70 leading-relaxed font-inter\">Nuestro corporativo proporciona dirección estratégica, asignación de capital y recursos compartidos, permitiendo a nuestras divisiones enfocarse puramente en transformar sus respectivos mercados.</p><a class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-[#A65E44] hover:text-[#F28F6B] hover:gap-4 transition-all uppercase tracking-widest text-sm\" href=\"/es/about\">Conoce nuestra visión<!-- --> <span>→</span></a></div></div></section><section class=\"py-32 px-6 bg-[#162D59]/5\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"text-center mb-24\"><h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6\">Liderazgo</h2><p class=\"text-xl text-neutral-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Guiados por operadores con un historial de retornos asimétricos.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12\"><div class=\"group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"aspect-[4/5] rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden mb-8 bg-neutral-100 relative\"><img alt=\"Josue\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097027-c1d30f71ad39%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097027-c1d30f71ad39%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097027-c1d30f71ad39%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097027-c1d30f71ad39%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097027-c1d30f71ad39%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097027-c1d30f71ad39%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097027-c1d30f71ad39%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097027-c1d30f71ad39%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097027-c1d30f71ad39%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097027-c1d30f71ad39%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1560250097027-c1d30f71ad39%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-2\">Josue</h3><div class=\"text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400 mb-4\">Director Ejecutivo</div><p class=\"text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed\">Arquitecto del ecosistema Arasue. Se enfoca en la asignación de capital y la visión a largo plazo.</p></div><div class=\"group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"aspect-[4/5] rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden mb-8 bg-neutral-100 relative\"><img alt=\"Elena M.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1573496359142-b8d87734a5a2%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1573496359142-b8d87734a5a2%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1573496359142-b8d87734a5a2%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1573496359142-b8d87734a5a2%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1573496359142-b8d87734a5a2%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1573496359142-b8d87734a5a2%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1573496359142-b8d87734a5a2%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1573496359142-b8d87734a5a2%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1573496359142-b8d87734a5a2%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1573496359142-b8d87734a5a2%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1573496359142-b8d87734a5a2%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-2\">Elena M.</h3><div class=\"text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400 mb-4\">Directora de Forge</div><p class=\"text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed\">Ex ingeniera principal en importantes firmas tecnológicas. Lidera la ingeniería de productos y la escala de la plataforma.</p></div><div class=\"group\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\"><div class=\"aspect-[4/5] rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden mb-8 bg-neutral-100 relative\"><img alt=\"Marcus T.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 33vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.unsplash.com%2Fphoto-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d%3Fq%3D80%26w%3D600%26auto%3Dformat%26fit%3Dcrop&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-2\">Marcus T.</h3><div class=\"text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-neutral-400 mb-4\">Director de Media</div><p class=\"text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed\">Estratega cultural que ha fabricado múltiples momentos virales globales.</p></div></div></div></section><section id=\"portfolio\" class=\"py-32 px-6 bg-[#F2F2F2]\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10\"><div class=\"text-center mb-20\"><h2 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-playfair tracking-tight mb-6 text-[#162D59]\">El Ecosistema Arasue</h2><p class=\"text-xl text-[#162D59]/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-inter\">Cinco divisiones interconectadas impulsando el momento cultural y comercial.</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8\"><a href=\"/es/forge\"><div class=\"group relative h-[320px] rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden bg-[#162D59]/[0.02] border border-[#162D59]/10 p-10 flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-[#162D59]/20 hover:bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-[15px] transition-all duration-500 shadow-[0_8px_32px_0_rgba(22,45,89,0.05)]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0511F2] to-[#05F2DB] opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 rounded-full blur-[60px] transition-opacity duration-700 -mr-20 -mt-20\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-playfair font-bold mb-4 text-[#162D59]\">Arasue Forge</h3><p class=\"text-[#162D59]/70 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md font-inter\">Las grandes ideas no sirven de nada si se quedan en el aire. Arasue Forge es el estudio de desarrollo donde el software avanzado y la tecnología crítica cobran vida con precisión, fuerza y un rendimiento impecable.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#162D59]/50 group-hover:text-[#162D59] transition-colors relative z-10\">Explore Division<span class=\"ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform\">→</span></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 border-2 border-transparent group-hover:border-[#A65E44]/20 rounded-[2rem] pointer-events-none transition-colors duration-500\"></div></div></a><a href=\"/es/media\"><div class=\"group relative h-[320px] rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden bg-[#162D59]/[0.02] border border-[#162D59]/10 p-10 flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-[#162D59]/20 hover:bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-[15px] transition-all duration-500 shadow-[0_8px_32px_0_rgba(22,45,89,0.05)]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#F28F6B] to-[#A65E44] opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 rounded-full blur-[60px] transition-opacity duration-700 -mr-20 -mt-20\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-playfair font-bold mb-4 text-[#162D59]\">Arasue Media</h3><p class=\"text-[#162D59]/70 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md font-inter\">En un mar de ruido constante, nosotros creamos profundidad. Arasue Media produce, edita y distribuye contenido de alta fidelidad que captura la atención y deja una marca real.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#162D59]/50 group-hover:text-[#162D59] transition-colors relative z-10\">Explore Division<span class=\"ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform\">→</span></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 border-2 border-transparent group-hover:border-[#A65E44]/20 rounded-[2rem] pointer-events-none transition-colors duration-500\"></div></div></a><a href=\"/es/labs\"><div class=\"group relative h-[320px] rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden bg-[#162D59]/[0.02] border border-[#162D59]/10 p-10 flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-[#162D59]/20 hover:bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-[15px] transition-all duration-500 shadow-[0_8px_32px_0_rgba(22,45,89,0.05)]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1a2e1a] to-emerald-800 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 rounded-full blur-[60px] transition-opacity duration-700 -mr-20 -mt-20\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-playfair font-bold mb-4 text-[#162D59]\">Arasue Labs</h3><p class=\"text-[#162D59]/70 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md font-inter\">La verdadera excelencia no acepta atajos. Arasue Labs une el rigor de la ciencia con la pureza de la naturaleza, controlando la importación y logística de productos premium con una trazabilidad absoluta.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#162D59]/50 group-hover:text-[#162D59] transition-colors relative z-10\">Explore Division<span class=\"ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform\">→</span></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 border-2 border-transparent group-hover:border-[#A65E44]/20 rounded-[2rem] pointer-events-none transition-colors duration-500\"></div></div></a><a href=\"/es/protection\"><div class=\"group relative h-[320px] rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden bg-[#162D59]/[0.02] border border-[#162D59]/10 p-10 flex flex-col justify-between hover:border-[#162D59]/20 hover:bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-[15px] transition-all duration-500 shadow-[0_8px_32px_0_rgba(22,45,89,0.05)]\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#162D59] to-slate-500 opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 rounded-full blur-[60px] transition-opacity duration-700 -mr-20 -mt-20\"></div><div class=\"relative z-10\"><h3 class=\"text-3xl font-playfair font-bold mb-4 text-[#162D59]\">Arasue Protection</h3><p class=\"text-[#162D59]/70 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-md font-inter\">El éxito real no se deja al azar. Arasue Protection blinda tu vida, tu salud y tu patrimonio con soluciones de aseguramiento de alto nivel y total certeza.</p></div><div class=\"flex items-center text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#162D59]/50 group-hover:text-[#162D59] transition-colors relative z-10\">Explore Division<span class=\"ml-2 transform group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform\">→</span></div><div class=\"absolute inset-0 border-2 border-transparent group-hover:border-[#A65E44]/20 rounded-[2rem] pointer-events-none transiti